    <p class="sec-lead">
      Venezuela&rsquo;s oil infrastructure was designed for a 3M+&nbsp;bpd industry.
      Years of underinvestment have left most facilities operating well below
      nameplate capacity &mdash; an estimated ~35% utilization across the refining
      complex.
    </p>

